text: I went to see this movie last night with a couple of friends out of boredom and curiosity. We all had really bad expectations but it was a pleasant surprise. There's callbacks to episodes from 10 years ago, humor that appeals to people above 5 years old and the ending made the whole experience awesome. It's a victim of terrible advertising, since the subtitle is "Sponge Out Of Water" but it's totally false. Only 20 to 25 minutes were on the surface. There's a pirate that's narrating it, but it's not Patchy The Pirate. Do yourself a favor and watch this movie, the pirate/narrator ties into a mystery that many fans have been curious about since the first episode. Please, don't get the wrong idea because of the terrible advertising campaign.
